{"tid":1590292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買唔到蘋果特刊手足唔洗失望","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:27:51.000Z","uid":299254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9475321ac2d32cb9d74512275e6442ecb25d45","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之前一個二個仆曬去買蘋果特刊<br />\n行左好多間都買唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而外國勢力times magazine 呢<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n今日行hysan誠品仲有8月26號出嘅times賣<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4fSUFGf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fSUFGf.png&h=49903b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">封面個手足好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出版左就快一個月但竟然仲有咁多本賣唔出</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONMaYtb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONMaYtb.png&h=3d7305a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">買唔到蘋果嘅手足可以考慮買番本作紀念<br />\n希望行過唔會仲見到賣剩咁多本</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻同我清曬佢！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"314cc77a3a06faeb28b38048591dc1d02e79ca2b","tid":1590292,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"c37cbd3f862b254927543fe4949067b9bf4f9cc8","tid":1590292,"uid":201649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840247187e951c272060a841c847ae0279aefa4e","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"98fa3d73ef0f032d4853ca5fd17b1ff363a15e04","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"d96476f3777b749c2a4a71cd577a0441cc35eaac","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"a1c60f99e55284599f8d7020bb0b0936a3c64067","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"06e9f47464f576b5f22427afb1d0a3e5f7de47d4","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"6d538d5a2e7a3e7c758db3f3e49c090a8945331b","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"7308d82c5f905644770df843dc37004895e32f4c","tid":1590292,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"革